║ DIRECTORY LAYOUT                                                              ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

data_raw/        → Immutable source data (Planck, SH0ES, TRGB, TDCOSMO)
data_encoded/    → UHA binary/JSON outputs
analysis/        → Results, tension geometry, systematic targets
src/             → Source code (constants, cosmology, encode, decode, etc.)
notebooks/       → Jupyter analysis notebooks
tests/           → Unit and regression tests
SAID/            → Scientific integrity protocols ⭐
scripts/         → Automation (run_all.sh, verify_crc, checksums)
manifests/       → Metadata, checksums, changelog

